{"tid":1550310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每晚2230 播香港國歌","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:08:25.000Z","uid":19880,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a56d4fc6bda4d58303c82fe375abd5b8c29b9a57","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"《願榮光歸香港》呢首歌我自己聽既時候就已經覺得佢真係可以做到香港國歌<br />\n呢個idea 就係希望將呢首歌傳比每一個人<br />\n想身邊既人識唱一定要聽得多 如果可以大家仲可以一齊唱<br />\n只要每晚2230 用自己最大聲既喇叭 對住出面播國歌，慢慢每個人都會識唱！"},{"pid":"c0af32fc734ba981f08f4d43b5505aaa07bfe9f8","tid":1550310,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:30:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68fc72b7d19d2d422984b0c6382c8fe0ec54e18c","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa7cce1d51c80d667d36c633b3204c851200050c","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:30:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"181081e558e4394db4f21cb9dca6713fce427b3f","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0d115432cf8f832ae0c38c649d4741bc11c78a2b","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"自己推10次"},{"pid":"6c3b090793c570346eb3a391f02974dbdf81dcac","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:31:42.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"9246403591d2ffe8569b2bf5600fccc11b8cc2a0","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"d938b1d70b71da0ece00c405bc615e05a35c38e9","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"157c5fbed0c7664d7c2c9963354ad214e6e9c27c","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:18.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"efb7fd294f473dce06b15c3c168c5fec72bed57d","tid":1550310,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n第二樣野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住為美國風災祈禱：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「多里安」Dorian <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在美國造成最少4人死亡</span></span>，南、北卡州超過35萬戶停電。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=e3af71eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&h=d997d1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2019/09/05/b6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04/thumbnail/620x349/8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4/0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbsnews1.cbsistatic.com%2Fhub%2Fi%2Fr%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2Fb6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04%2Fthumbnail%2F620x349%2F8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4%2F0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg&h=6aa446ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國歌(快d聽熟！) 、揮<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國旗！！！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=25643680\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"49424d09a1ba16a4d106267e63f98cc7e5c1fb23","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"9d34433cc2bf3d752a736d283f9a8fc1b634e5e4","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:42.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"b0699cc30f50b2e99de316adb7fc58b881f6bf8a","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"a09b9f9c60776eb14f7cd8fbe4de72060885f3b3","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:33:04.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"146fb3d7d84fa8f56622796c8d0276c17f33a0d8","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"f9d52bc84c74f80c819dfb19bc1137bad932f426","tid":1550310,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:33:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有集會開始前，應先唱頌或奏《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n參加者應當起立，肅立致敬<br />\n右手置於心胸前<br />\n任何非宗教的頭飾應摘除並放置於左肩</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQQpnEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQQpnEV.png&h=d7a5b483&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a59bc9e4c44704ae2aaf3b4658dad0514909855","tid":1550310,"uid":250356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"好有歸屬感 香港國歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕推"},{"pid":"7f329320bf3f36f618fcb3a7484e48d7baadbb34","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:33:37.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c9f4c89dbac22d5f66dc4df08bffc2f9ee1e418e","tid":1550310,"uid":314504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:06.000Z","msg":"基本法寫明2007-08年香港有普選，現在香港人只是在要求原本應有但被中共反口所奪取了的自治權。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會將會審議通過的《香港人權及民主法案》便是借助美國的監督之下使香港有普選，獲得原本應有的自治權。<br />\n<br />\n故此，渴望民主普選多年的香港人，沒理由不支持《香港人權及民主法案》的通過了吧？<br />\n<br />\n不支持／要求修改／削弱法案通過的就都是鬼，是賣港賊。除此之外，再沒有更合理的理由去辯解了吧？<br />\n<br />\n只要有普選，透過民選的議會修憲完善自治權，香港便能和平演變，無需宣佈獨立都已是一個主權接近完整（無名有實）的獨立國家，就如加拿大（自治領）和紐西蘭（自治領）這些英聯邦國家一樣。<br />\n<br />\n驅逐共黨<br />\n光復香港<br />\n<br />\n#LiberateHK<br />\n#香港憲法保衛戰<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6C6Pz0Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6C6Pz0Z.jpg&h=8efb32f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8c13e37e5b16c43806e9fa1a9289e480dc17953","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:35:07.000Z","msg":"真係唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efe3b824091bf42b02eb28bf1b69e57b62fe8f2","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"推吵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2229cff26fcf3f9a2f772f6c249cb8fca5fb9753","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:39:01.000Z","msg":"比正評既巴絲幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67cbd767167b10d5df806c926515f651e8c5467","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5313dfbe1a3dc20d125ae9a94eb437cf354fa336","tid":1550310,"uid":19880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"推"}]}